" Auto indent

set autoindent
set smartindent

" Map auto complite of (, {

:imap ( ()<esc>i
:imap { {<esc>o}<esc>O
:imap [ []<esc>i

" position curseur

set ruler

" Highlight

:highlight ExtraWhitespace ctermbg=red guibg=red
:match ExtraWhitespace /\s\+$\| \+\ze\t\| \s\s/
